    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be an excellent choice for a buyer looking for a solid project or a budget-friendly option. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, it starts and runs, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to bring it back to peak performance. It\u2019s a reliable workhorse that just needs a little TLC.",
      "price": 24500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
